---
title: Chipotle Fish Tacos with Pineapple Salsa and Creamy Slaw
description: Taco night just got tastier! Flaky barramundi is coated in smoky chipotle and broiled for a spicy, charred filling. Top with a pile of creamy coleslaw and sweet-savoury pineapple salsa for the perfect handheld!
